        "role": "assistant",
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Thanks \u2014 a couple more to fill the gaps before I can build this.\n\n**Existing property loans**\n- QLD: current loan balance?\n- VIC: current loan balance?\n- NT: current loan balance?\n\n**Cash available**\n- How much deposit/cash do you have sitting ready to deploy (outside of equity)?\n\n**Commercial property**\n- Target price range, or happy for me to use a default?\n- State preference?\n\n**Granny flat funding**\n- Drawing equity from the VIC property, or funding from cash savings?",
